<div class="text-center">
  <div class="row justify-content-center align-items-center">
    <div class="col-md-6">
      <h2 class="my-4">Gymbuds: Just a Swipe Away â€“ Match, Message, Meet!</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6">
      <%= image_tag("gymbuds-logo.png", alt: "Gym Buds Logo", class: "img-fluid my-3", width: "200") %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<% if !user_signed_in? %>
  <div class="d-flex justify-content-center my-4">
    <%= link_to "Get Started", new_user_registration_path, class: "btn btn-lg btn-primary mx-2", role: "button" %>
    <%= button_to "Sign In", new_user_session_path, class: "btn btn-lg btn-danger mx-2", role: "button" %>
  </div>
<% end %>

<div class="d-flex flex-row justify-content-center flex-wrap">
  <div class="card mx-2 my-2" style="width: 18rem; background-color: #825DA7; color: white;">
    <div class="card-body">
      <h5 class="card-title">Match</h5>
      <p class="card-text">Swipe through profiles and look for your potential gym buddy.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card mx-2 my-2" style="width: 18rem; background-color: #5BABB6; color: white;">
    <div class="card-body">
      <h5 class="card-title">Message</h5>
      <p class="card-text">Found a match? It's time to chat! Share goals, tips, and plan your first gym meet-up.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card mx-2 my-2" style="width: 18rem; background-color: #5BB695; color: white;">
    <div class="card-body">
      <h5 class="card-title">Meet</h5>
      <p class="card-text">Sync schedules, pick a spot, and let the gains begin!</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="container">
  <div class="row">
    <!-- Carousel Column -->
    <div class="col-md-6">
      <div id="testimonialCarousel" class="carousel slide" data-bs-ride="carousel">
        <div class="carousel-inner">
          <div class="carousel-item active">
            <div class="card text-center">
              <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">John & Jane</h5>
                <p class="card-text">"Joining Gymbuds helped us find the motivation we needed. Together, we've overcome our gym fears and are now regulars, pushing each other every day!"</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="carousel-item">
            <div class="card text-center">
              <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">Mike & Emma</h5>
                <p class="card-text">"Finding each other through Gymbuds was a game-changer. It's easier to wake up for a 5 AM workout when you know your buddy is counting on you!"</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="carousel-item">
            <div class="card text-center">
              <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">Alice & Bob</h5>
                <p class="card-text">"We were both hesitant about going to the gym alone, but Gymbuds brought us together. Now, we're not just gym partners but great friends too!"</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="carousel-item">
            <div class="card text-center">
              <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">Sophia & Grace </h5>
                <p class="card-text">"After Sophia was diagnosed with diabetes, we both decided it was time for a change. Gymbuds helped us connect, and together, we've managed to take control of our health with regular exercise."</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="carousel-item">
            <div class="card text-center">
              <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">Aiden & Jacob </h5>
                <p class="card-text">"What started as a weekly workout session through Gymbuds turned into a strong friendship. We're more than gym partners; we're best friends, always there to support each other in and out of the gym."</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
        <button class="carousel-control-prev" type="button" data-bs-target="#testimonialCarousel" data-bs-slide="prev">
          <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span class="visually-hidden">Previous</span>
        </button>
        <button class="carousel-control-next" type="button" data-bs-target="#testimonialCarousel" data-bs-slide="next">
          <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span class="visually-hidden">Next</span>
        </button>
      </div>

      <%= content_tag :iframe, nil, src: "https://player.vimeo.com/video/940901549", width: 640, height: 360, frameborder: 0, allowfullscreen: true %>
    </div>

    <!-- Contact Form Column -->
    <div class="col-md-6">

      <div class="container">
        <div class="mx-auto my-5 p-5 bg-white rounded shadow-sm" style="max-width: 500px;">
          <div class="text-center">
            <h1 class="h3 mb-3 font-weight-normal text-dark">Contact Us</h1>
            <p class="text-muted">Fill up the form below to send us a message.</p>
          </div>
          <form action="https://api.web3forms.com/submit" method="POST" id="form">
            <input type="hidden" name="access_key" value="0ca041b5-7c2c-473f-80ce-951c798054c9">
            <input type="hidden" name="subject" value="New Submission from Web3Forms">
            <input type="checkbox" name="botcheck" id="" style="display: none;">
            <div class="mb-3">
              <label for="name" class="form-label">Full Name</label>
              <input type="text" name="name" id="name" placeholder="John Doe" required class="form-control">
            </div>
            <div class="mb-3">
              <label for="email" class="form-label">Email Address</label>
              <input type="email" name="email" id="email" placeholder="you@example.com" required class="form-control">
            </div>
            <div class="mb-3">
              <label for="phone" class="form-label">Phone Number</label>
              <input type="text" name="phone" id="phone" placeholder="+1 (555) 1234-567" required class="form-control">
            </div>
            <div class="mb-3">
              <label for="message" class="form-label">Your Message</label>
              <textarea rows="5" name="message" id="message" placeholder="Type your message..." required class="form-control"></textarea>
            </div>
            <div class="mb-3">
              <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-block">Send Message</button>
            </div>
          </form>
          <script src="path/to/form.js"></script>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</div>
